# 8. Challenges & Limitations

## Challenges

SSL certificate hostname mismatch during Nikto scan.

Incorrect VPC configuration caused Bastion connectivity issues.

Datadog agent required reinstall due to API configuration error.

---

## Limitations

Use of free tools:

- Nmap
- Nikto
- Wordfence free edition

Manual hardening could introduce human error.

Production environments would require:

- Nessus
- BurpSuite Pro
- AWS WAF
- automated patch management.

